 be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c488dbdaaa2732ce8ce662dd7af52d2c3d34f377","tid":1753602,"uid":42487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:41:24.000Z","msg":"一貫支那作風<br />\n永遠一定係人地錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd325c3b7b5c2377505464c25337a881e85aa11","tid":1753602,"uid":305358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:43:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，死不悔改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de48da7055cc3bb4ec9086f5d2046e43c11828ec","tid":1753602,"uid":108462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:43:28.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"11fb9e457f05a72a8d611dc937390c5f016b73df","tid":1753602,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:44:24.000Z","msg":"輸就輸啦，仲講埋呢d野呃大陸錢加推責任。<br />\n睇睇決戰中途島，打輸杖既司令會點做？"},{"pid":"b83ee6c3bd44beb8b521b5a2d5190fd5eca6ff5f","tid":1753602,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c488dbdaaa2732ce8ce662dd7af52d2c3d34f377","tid":1753602,"uid":42487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:41:24.000Z","msg":"一貫支那作風<br />\n永遠一定係人地錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:58:42.000Z","msg":"總之千錯萬錯一定係人哋錯"},{"pid":"0400d19925d801d21322c995d92fb6a94126c9fa","tid":1753602,"uid":119596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:00:19.000Z","msg":"響度兜得咁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賴地硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6626bf9f645eada74a9c3b96e815e1a3c9e0dee4","tid":1753602,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:00:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e4291ec0b1155ac11d94a818d9ca09c9629fd3a","tid":1753602,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c488dbdaaa2732ce8ce662dd7af52d2c3d34f377","